reviewText:
we used to watch Wil Quack Quack when my twenty something was a wee one. Nothing gave her more fun, at least inside! Recommend for children who do not need lots of noise and clatter for entertainment. Too bad it does not seem to be on DVDs. Maybe if we ask and ask, someone will produce one. I did find a couple of episodes on YouTube.

Wil Cwac Cwac - Title ImageWil Cwac Cwac or Will Quack Quack
